# Bayanihan-Net runs fully offline by default. No secrets are required to reproduce
# the worked scenario, evaluation, stress tests, or the RL routing study.
#
# These variables only affect the OPTIONAL live-LLM enrichment layer (Tier B), which
# is never on the safety-critical path. Copy this file to `.env` if you want it.

# --- Optional: cloud LLM enrichment (Tier B) ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-5.4-mini

# --- Optional: local LLM enrichment (Tier B) ---
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
# OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.1

# Never commit a real key. .env is gitignored. If a key was shared while building,
# rotate it at the provider console.
